    {
      "title": "Setup Instructions",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 20 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## RAGAS Dashboard Setup\n\n1. Run RAGAS evaluation: `make eval-ragas`\n2. Report saved to `./tmp/eval/ragas_report.json`\n3. Install Grafana JSON API plugin: `grafana-cli plugins install marcusolsson-json-datasource`\n4. Add JSON API datasource pointing to the report file URL\n5. Update panel targets to use the datasource\n\n### Metrics\n- **Faithfulness**: Factual consistency with retrieved context (0-1)\n- **Answer Relevancy**: How relevant the answer is to the question (0-1)\n- **Context Precision**: Proportion of relevant retrieved contexts (0-1)\n- **Answer Correctness**: Semantic similarity with ground truth (0-1)\n\n### Thresholds\n- 🟢 Green: ≥ 0.75 (good)\n- 🟡 Orange: 0.50–0.75 (needs improvement)\n- 🔴 Red: < 0.50 (poor)"
      }
